{"tid":4091,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"個人親身經歷, 千其唔好買華為電話!!!!!","createTime":"2016-11-26T11:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T04:05:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"187f211ae81e4021a549d30ed2eeffb30cad1745","tid":4091,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"所有大陸品牌電話, 不論硬件或軟件, 或兩者兼而有之, 在出廠前已經安裝了監控程式, 這是中國政府的內部要求, 已經是行業內的公開秘密, 一些中外合資的如alcatel 可能例外, 但為免麻煩, 建議還是不要用, 至於什麼小米聯想鬼族中興華為等等等等, 可以明確告訴大家, 百分之一百已經植入監控程式, 毫無例外, 至於今天小米才被人發覺, 可能是行家為了打擊其銷量的一種手段. <br />\n<br />\n一句話, 所有大陸品牌電話全部都不要用. <br />\n<br />\n你是普通人不怕, 但你的聯絡人的聯絡人可能不是普通人, 可能就因為你用了大陸品牌電話而被監控竊密, 間接害了人. 正如前段時間香港公投, 被發現不少襲擊來源是一般中移動電話用戶及其家用電腦, 自己被共匪利用來做壞事都不知道.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#good2#15  #bad#2 <br />\n<br />\n標籤： Reply  Reply  Reply  Reply 21/11/2016 2:45"},{"pid":"d615790825f06ceb93b28f904db9f25c7664ef0a","tid":4091,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5e34e83dce4173c6448463becb688b6925df6e","tid":4091,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44b2ba292c8723b0a519359bf75d651b58f550a","tid":4091,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa9b66365bf7d1d8d2942f5317d7f6fca368aab","tid":4091,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef45ab70f758510a429dc930d511ecb3aaa3aff8","tid":4091,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"同成班 ifanboy 講有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d400